result.name: SLC7A10 variant causal for paradoxical pseudo myotonia in English Spaniels
result.description: The recessive c.126C>A(p.(Cys42Ter) SLC7A10 nonsense variant causes paradoxical pseudomyotonia in English Springer and Cocker Spaniels.
result.center: Department of Veterinary and Biosciences, Faculty of Veterinary Medicine, Ghent University
